---
import ActivityPageBase from "../../layouts/ActivityPageBase.astro";

---

<ActivityPageBase title="活動介紹" eventImage="/images/banner/match_arena.png">
    
    <div slot="introduction-text">
    <h2>遊戲規則:</h2>
<p>每回合開始時把地板的顔色記起來</p>
<p>牆上顯示顔色後地板將不會有顔色</p>
<p>憑記憶站到正確的顔色上, 最後一人為勝者</p>
<p>畫面上方的BOSS血條代表各階段的時間</p>
</div>
    <div slot="win-reward">
        <h2>勝利獎勵</h2>
        <img src="/images/items/match-winner.png" alt="勝利獎勵圖示" class="winner-image"> 
    </div>
</ActivityPageBase>

<style>
    
    .winner-image{
        max-width: 100%;
    } 
</style>
